data.title: Health & Wellness Navigators
data.meta_description: Our Customer Care Navigators guide you through the Tahoe Forest Health System. Customers Care Navigators want you to be satisfied with your patient experience.
data.text:
Our Health & Wellness Navigators guide local residents and area visitors through Tahoe Forest Health System. Health & Wellness Navigators make it simple and want you to be satisfied with your patient experience.

The navigators can guide you to the appropriate physician, program, or service that fits your needs, including:

Tahoe Forest Health System providers or hospital departments

Community health care providers, wellness programs, and resources

Call us with questions or if you are in need of assistance! (530) 587-3769
